.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: grey, brown, azure, chestnut, purple
There are 5 different nationalities: american, argentine, japanese, pakistani, egyptian
There are 5 different favourite beverages: lemonade, cola, fanta, almond-milk, hot-chocolate
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: greymaster, game, montecristo, siglo, bolivar
5 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, pony, turtle, mouse, rabbit
1. the american is the person who likes azure
2. the swedish is the owner of the turtle
3. the argentine is the person drinking almond-milk
4. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes chestnut
5. the person who likes brown is the person drinking cola
6. the montecristo-smoker is the owner of the pony
7. the person who likes purple is the game-smoker
8. the person drinking fanta is in the middle
9. the pakistani is on the far left
10. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig
11. the owner of the rabbits is on the left or right of the game-smoker
12. the greymaster-smoker is the person drinking lemonade
13. the japanese is the siglo-smoker
14. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person who likes grey
15. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    purple	|     grey	|      azure	|     brown	|     chestnut	|
| Nationality	|   pakistani	|    argentine	|    american	|    japanese	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     guinea-pig	|    rabbit	|     pony	|     mouse	|      turtle	|
| Beverage	|    hot-chocolate	|     almond-milk	|     fanta	|    cola	|      lemonade	|
| Cigar		|   game	|    bolivar	|  montecristo	|    siglo	|   greymaster	|
